Package: BCFM
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Clustering Factor Model for Clustering and Factor Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Allison", "Tegge", email = "ategge@vt.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Marco", "Ferreira", email = "marf@vt.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Hwasoo", "Shin", email = "hshin2@hfhs.org", role = "aut"),
    person("Meriem", "Touami", email = "meriemt@vt.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Implements Bayesian Clustering Factor Model (BCFM) for clustering 
    and latent factor analysis of multivariate longitudinal data. Provides model 
    selection tools, MCMC sampling via Rcpp, and comprehensive visualization functions 
    for exploring cluster assignments, factor loadings, and model diagnostics.
License: GPL (>= 3)
